        "text": "rOpenSci's next Social Coworking and office hours is up in two weeks :tada:\n\nThese are casual online events for coworking and socializing generally centred on a theme related to R and tools for open\/reproducible science.\nYou can work quietly on your own, join in a discussion, or work while listening to the discussion, what ever suits you (and you don't have to follow the theme).\n\n:grey_exclamation: Theme: Debugging in R\n:hourglass_flowing_sand: When: Tuesday July 7th 09:00 Americas Pacific (16:00 UTC)\n:cookie: Hosted by: <@U01ERR6MN9G> and co-host <@U051BH4JSS3>\n:mag: Details: <https:\/\/ropensci.org\/events\/coworking-2026-07>\n\nYou can use this time for...\n- General coworking\n- Read up on debugging in R\n- Cowork independently on something related to R\n- Chat with Shannon Pileggi and other attendees about our theme!",
